org.eclipse.egf.pattern
Interface PatternPackage.Literals

Enclosing interface:
PatternPackage
public static interface PatternPackage.Literals

Defines literals for the meta objects that represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
